text: Homole may refer to: *Homolium or Homole, a town of ancient Thessaly, Greece *Homole (České Budějovice District), a village and municipality in the Czech Republic *Homole, former name of Homole u Panny, a village and municipality in the Czech Republic *Homole, a castle in Lower Silesian Voivodeship, Poland
title: Homole
